Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.55,0:22:30.29,ed_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}你的名字
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.29,0:22:33.83,ed_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}無論發生什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:22:34.63,0:22:36.43,ed_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}我都會從容呼喚
Dialogue: 1,0:22:47.43,0:22:52.42,ed_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}你有一顆長滿荊刺的內心
Dialogue: 1,0:22:52.90,0:22:57.84,ed_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}傷害著觸碰自己的一切
Dialogue: 1,0:22:58.14,0:23:03.10,ed_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}瞪眼怒視著世間的所有
Dialogue: 1,0:23:03.10,0:23:05.86,ed_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}你的目光在訴說
Dialogue: 1,0:23:05.86,0:23:08.51,ed_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}我就在這裡
Dialogue: 1,0:23:08.51,0:23:13.49,ed_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}有誰笑了
Dialogue: 1,0:23:13.93,0:23:16.35,ed_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}所以你劃出了
Dialogue: 1,0:23:16.52,0:23:18.84,ed_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}那條境界線
Dialogue: 1,0:23:19.19,0:23:24.03,ed_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}既然這樣 就由我來
Dialogue: 1,0:23:24.09,0:23:27.48,ed_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}牽著你的手
Dialogue: 1,0:23:28.52,0:23:33.04,ed_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}帶你一起去
Dialogue: 1,0:23:35.51,0:23:39.15,ed_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}如果說不出口
Dialogue: 1,0:23:39.53,0:23:44.35,ed_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}就緊緊地握住我的手
Dialogue: 1,0:23:44.73,0:23:46.31,ed_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}不要放開
Dialogue: 1,0:23:46.31,0:23:54.52,ed_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}你如今已經不是孤身一人
